<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ginger249-jackie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4136896); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4136896&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610222201" alt="Ginger249-Jackie" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4136896)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ginger249-jackie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4136896); return false;">Ginger249-Jackie</a></span></p>
